ate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T05:23:16.000Z","msg":"佢國藉係美利堅喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4480f54e0be97e2a876b612e16767f51fdafa266","tid":1089760,"uid":155682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T05:31:20.000Z","msg":"估唔到萬世師表嘅後人，去到20世紀，竟然會捨棄中華文化，轉為推崇東洋文化，連個女嘅名都參考返日本古藉，証明中華文化已沒落。"},{"pid":"a7f7f40d91eee129b6ad82a74b7d4a983268f4cc","tid":1089760,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:27:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.acliving.net/a/meihuazixun/wenhuayishu/2019/0105/26776.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.acliving.net%2Fa%2Fmeihuazixun%2Fwenhuayishu%2F2019%2F0105%2F26776.html&d=hsG%2BTWPyVhMSOc%2FhwZgu%2BiaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=6db89b9f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.acliving.net/a/meihuazixun/wenhuayishu/2019/0105/26776.html</a><br />\n<br />\n提到孔子自然而然想起大華府山東同鄉會兩天前剛舉辦的祭孔大典。趙小蘭部長說，很遺憾她不知道消息，不然至少會送個祝辭。談祭孔，自然提及孔子第76代直系嫡孫女孔令和女士。趙部長馬上關心地問Auntie Anita （孔令和婚後名字為董孔令和，英文名Anita Tong）的近况。"},{"pid":"3cb69f33d4799334546d9b52c2c3fb97de0cdc4d","tid":1089760,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:28:27.000Z","msg":"反日糞青又有新目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb55d673f77ee4b4bc254e78ea10d9e297a3bcb8","tid":1089760,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:55:37.000Z","msg":"孔子係日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}